      <title>韩国将积极应对选举后市场波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/korea-vows-active-response-to-post-us-election-market-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国表示，将加强对金融市场的监控，并“积极”应对，以缓解过度波动，因为政策制定者正在为唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫的影响做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/korea-vows-active-response-to-post-us-election-market-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
